---
title: Seared Garlic Butter Steak with Roast Veggie Toss & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Simple and sensational – they're the buzzwords for tonight's dinner. A tender cut of beef eye with a creamy pesto dressing,
golden roasted veggies and an aromatic garlic butter combine to make a special meal that'll have you buzzing too!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
